{
  "$comment": "PawsOff ConsentGhost - remote CMP selector config. Host this on Cloudflare Pages (e.g. https://config.getpawsoff.app/consent-ghost/consent-config.json) alongside its detached signature consent-config.json.sig (see scripts/sign-config.js). The content script's BUNDLED_CONSENT_CONFIG in src/content/consent-ghost.js is the offline/first-run mirror of this file - keep them in sync. background.js fetches + ECDSA-P256-verifies this before the content script will use it; any failure falls open to the bundled copy.",
